title: Stock market news live updates: Stock futures little changed after S&P 500, Dow, and Nasdaq end losing streak - Yahoo Finance
content: Stock market news live updates: Stock futures little changed after S&P 500, Dow, and Nasdaq end losing streak  Yahoo Finance
description: U.S. equity futures were flat heading into overnight trading Wednesday after stocks capped a streak of downturn to log their best session in two years.
